{"_path":"/councilor/service/s2052","_dir":"service","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"607公車成功增班，4/11起正式上路！","description":null,"image":"/images/service/s2052-1.png","sequence":2052,"category1":"A. 健全都市發展","category2":"A.4 強化區域交通規劃","link":"https://www.facebook.com/share/p/18WvumwTLJ/","author":"李宗豪","head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":"李宗豪"},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口-社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2025-03-18T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"_607-公車成功增班411-起正式上路"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"607 公車成功增班，4/11 起正式上路！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"好消息！宗豪過去積極向市府爭取，607 公車加開班次終於核定！預計新增 6 個班次，讓大家通勤更便利。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"除了 607 公車的增班，我也持續推動 603 公車加開班次，希望縮短候車時間，讓通勤更順暢。還有 606 公車的雙循環線規劃也在積極爭取中，希望提升重劃區內的公車路網，讓居民的大眾運輸選擇更多元。我也會持續爭取增設「文青國中小」公車站，讓學童與周邊居民通勤更便利。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"改善公共運輸是我一直關心的議題，宗豪會持續努力，讓龜山的交通更完善、更便利！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s2052-1.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s2052-1.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"上次臨時會我也建議 603、606、967 等公車增加尖峰時段班次，爭取更完善的交通服務！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s2052-2.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s2052-2.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在質詢交通局時，我也提到請交通局研議增設「文青國中小」公車站，未來不管是接送還是就學都更方便！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s2052-3.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s2052-3.jpeg"},"children":[]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"